      "visualDescription": "A vibrant 2D anime illustration showing a cozy living room scene. A family of three – Mom, Dad, and their young daughter Lily – are happily gathered around a small coffee table. They are playing a colorful board game, with game pieces and cards spread out. Lily, a cheerful young girl, sits between her parents, smiling brightly. Dad is laughing heartily, and Mom watches them with a warm, loving expression. Soft, warm sunlight streams through a large window in the background, showing a hint of a bright day outside. The room is decorated simply, evoking comfort and togetherness. The atmosphere is joyful and full of familial bliss. Clean line art and expressive faces.",
      "dialogueOrNarration": "The family is in the living room. Mom, Dad, and their daughter, Lily, are together. They play a board game. Lily smiles big. Dad laughs loud. Mom watches them with love. [warmly] The room is bright and cozy. A big window shows a sunny day. Everyone feels happy inside. They share snacks and juice. This is a special time for them. [softly] They talk and laugh a lot. They love each other very much. Family time is important. It brings much joy. They are a happy family always.",
      "subtitle": "The family is in the living room. Mom, Dad, and their daughter, Lily, are together. They play a board game. Lily smiles big. Dad laughs loud. Mom watches them with love. The room is bright and cozy. A big window shows a sunny day. Everyone feels happy inside. They share snacks and juice. This is a special time for them. They talk and laugh a lot. They love each other very much. Family time is important. It brings much joy. They are a happy family always.\nGia đình đang ở trong phòng khách. Mẹ, Bố và con gái của họ, Lily, đang ở cùng nhau. Họ chơi trò chơi cờ bàn. Lily cười rất tươi. Bố cười lớn tiếng. Mẹ nhìn họ với tình yêu. Căn phòng sáng sủa và ấm cúng. Một cửa sổ lớn cho thấy một ngày nắng đẹp. Mọi người đều cảm thấy vui vẻ bên trong. Họ cùng ăn vặt và uống nước trái cây. Đây là thời gian đặc biệt dành cho họ. Họ nói chuyện và cười rất nhiều. Họ yêu thương nhau rất nhiều. Thời gian dành cho gia đình rất quan trọng. Nó mang lại nhiều niềm vui. Họ luôn là một gia đình hạnh phúc.",
